How to determine the size of the Web? ... #pages, #hyperlinks

* get random selection of pages
* find how many are indexed by Google
* multiply Google index size by ratio

* look up DNS records (how many) ... estimate # sites
* count average pages on a selection of these
* multiply #records by avg pages

* relies on Google index
* counting publically reachable web
* blocked by robots.txt

* http://www.cse.unsw.edu.au/xyz?id=123
